verbose_text: First, using MTT assay, we found that pre-treatment with the autophagy inhibitor, 3-MA, or the autophagolysosome fusion inhibitor, CQ, significantly inhibited Adpa-Mn-induced cell death in a dose dependent manner (XREF_FIG).
evidence: autophagy inhibitor, 3-MA, or the autophagolysosome fusion inhibitor, CQ, significantly inhibited Adpa-Mn-induced cell death
